    "body": "> We have absolutly no tests that ensure that the array syntax works and we did not even used it once in our demos. I suggest we update all the jsdocs to only use {string}\n\n@pixelastic Careful we did discuss this in another issue and found out that it would be a lot of work to update everything. https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/432\n\nLet's not do this right now, there's no real need to do so?\n",
